gr-dvbldpc
======

Author: Ron Economos
Email: <w6rz@comcast.net>

The goal of this project is to build a GNU Radio block that implements
an LDPC decoder for the DVB-S2 and DVB-T2 standards. This project is a
port of the code in:

https://github.com/xdsopl/LDPC

The test Transport Stream can be downloaded from:

http://www.w6rz.net/thefuryclip.ts

Build instructions:

    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ../
    make
    sudo make install
    sudo ldconfig

Contributions are welcome!

